SUBJECT: Frontend Careers at Cargo.One
CONTENT: I am contacting you from cargo.one, a startup from Berlin that is digitalising the global air freight industry, building solutions for our partner freight forwarding companies and airline cargo carriers. Our business has responded to the pandemic by adopting a global remote first policy, and as such we are able to hire people in many international locations and throughout Germany.  https://www.cargo.one/  I would like to invite you to consider a role with us at cargo.one, specifically we have openings for the role of Senior Frontend Engineer (m/f/d). As an engineer at cargo.one you will be confronted with a wide spectrum of tasks. They range from collaborating with a variety of stakeholders, over designing features and taking architectural decisions to reviewing code of your peers and ensuring a good quality of our work. There's a really good paper by Microsoft Research called To Blob or Not To Blob.  Their conclusion after a large number of performance tests and analysis is this:  if your pictures or document are typically below 256KB in size, storing them in a database VARBINARY column is more efficient  if your pictures or document are typically over 1 MB in size, storing them in the filesystem is more efficient (and with SQL Server 2008's FILESTREAM attribute, they're still under transactional control and part of the database)

CONTENT: Dear Eduardo,   At first, thanks a lot for your attention. :)  Although I assume you are quite happy at TalentRocket, a new challenge as JavaScript  Webshop Engineer (m/f/d)  in Munich at Europe's biggest CE retailer, MediaMarktSaturn, could nevertheless be an appealing opportunity for you. With an eye on your remarkable experiences, the position could fit very well to your interests and skill-set.  So, what is currently going on at MediaMarktSaturn? Nothing less than a company-wide tech transformation towards an agile, product-centric setup. Consequently, there are a lot of new technologies and products continuously being developed. One of the most important objectives is to ramp up a fresh, state-of-the-art web shop (progressive web app) based on the Google Cloud Platform, with the aim to send the parallelly running webshop monolith into it's deserved retirement. Concludingly, the Shop Engineering Chapter plays a vital role in this setup - and we are looking for you to come on board, in our Munich office, where about 60 people are working in a Scrum setup.  Tech Stack: - JavaScript (ES6/ES7) - ReactJS - ReactNative - Redux - Typescript  - NodeJS  - GraphQL / Apollo - HTML5 - CSS - OAuth 2 - CI/CD - Webpack - PWAs - GCP (Private Alpha status) - Microservices - SPAs - Jest  What are your thoughts? Shouldn't we have a call in the next couple of days to further discuss this opportunity?  If this opportunity does not sound appealing, I would be nevertheless thankful if you would send me a short reply.  Best regards, and looking forward to hearing from you, Marc  P.S.: Here is a video  with our CTO Atul Bhardwaj about the tech transformation: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uO7Hjri0MRA   Marc Fritze Recruiter (ext.) / HR Business Partner Management MediaMarktSaturn Retail Group  +49 (841) 6344264 fritzema@mediamarktsaturn.com

Eduardo,Apenas 7% dos profissionais no Brasil receberam orientação profissional de um mentor. Nossas pesquisas indicam que, se receber aconselhamento fosse mais fácil, esse número seria mais alto. O LinkedIn agora oferece Aconselhamento Profissional, uma ferramenta gratuita, em que você pode receber orientação sob medida de profissionais e líderes experientes. Motivos para participar: Localizaremos os profissionais certos do seu setor para lhe ajudar Quando encontrarmos a pessoa ideal, você poderá entrar em contato com ela para conversar sobre a sua carreira   Nossa comunidade de profissionais pode ajudar você a ampliar sua rede ou aprender com alguém mais experiente Uma conversa pode transformar sua carreira. Ricardo Wright Gerente de Desenvolvimento de Negócios

Prezado Colega,Na CenturyLink, queremos poder apoiar o crescimento tecnológico das empresas, não só através dos nossos serviços, mas também fornecendo-lhes informações que podem ajudá-las a percorrer o caminho para a transformação digital.Através desta mensagem, convidamos você a baixar gratuitamente o nosso Whitepaper "Aceitando a Transformação Digital", onde se retratam uma série de processos importantes para se ter em conta ao encontrar e desenvolver tecnologias apropriadas, com base no contexto e a realidade da sua empresa. Esperamos que a informação seja útil e, como sempre, convidamos você a conhecer mais sobre nossas soluções clicando aqui.AtenciosamenteCenturyLink, América Latina
